{"tid":1851314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家係流動文宣嘅極佳時機","createTime":"2020-01-30T03:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T05:46:42.000Z","uid":185999,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"efd259f347787dd02bd4d9e1a2454501444e0508","tid":1851314,"uid":185999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"手足咁辛苦貼連儂<br />\n為嘅都係想中老年人停低睇下<br />\n而家度度都排隊買口罩<br />\n中年老人流 不滿情緒都齊曬<br />\n係千載難逢嘅好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺自己背囊/<br />\n條隊隔離拎住文宣show 出嚟<br />\n或者討論政府無能<br />\n又合法又安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 會唔會比藍屍打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA: 唔會，佢一離隊打你就要重新排過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家千祈唔好咁做，搞到人將矛頭指向政府係唔啱架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b39d6149bb12e74bf9cc564a58dd56d922bbf11","tid":1851314,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%